    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Two new troglobitic Coarazuphium Gnaspini, Godoy & Vanin 1998 species of ground beetles from iron ore Brazilian caves (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Zuphiini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845171>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845173>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845181>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845177> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845171>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Coarazuphium spinifemur new species, male holotype. (A) Habitus dorsal aspect. Scale bar = 0.5 mm. (B) Detail of hind wings. (C) Detail of metafemur spine." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/845171/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845173>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Coarazuphium spinifemur new species, male holotype. (A) Head, pronotum and prothorax, lateral aspect. (B) Prothorax, ventral aspect. Scale bars = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/845173/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845181>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Coarazuphium amazonicus new species, male holotype Aedeagus, (A) genital segment, left lateral aspect, (B) genital segment, left lateral aspect, (C) left lateral aspect, (D) dorsal aspect and (E) right lateral aspect. Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/845181/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.845177>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Coarazuphium amazonicus new species. (A) Habitus, dorsal aspect, male holotype. Scale bar = 1.0 mm. (B) Detail of hind wing, female paratype 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/845177/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

